---
const proFeatures = [
  'Web a medida y optimizada',
  'Integración WhatsApp Directo',
  'Sistema de Agendamiento (Calendly)',
  'Cambios ilimitados de contenido',
];

const fullFeatures = [
  { text: 'Todo lo incluido en Pro', icon: 'verified', highlight: true },
  { text: 'Gestión de Publicidad Online (Ads)', icon: 'check_circle', highlight: false },
  { text: 'SEO Básico y Avanzado', icon: 'check_circle', highlight: false },
  { text: 'Gestión Completa Google My Business', icon: 'check_circle', highlight: false },
  { text: 'Reportes mensuales de rendimiento', icon: 'check_circle', highlight: false },
];
---

<section id="planes" class="w-full py-16 lg:py-24 bg-[#0F1629] border-t border-slate-800">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-14">
      <h2 class="text-blue-400 font-bold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-2">Precios</h2>
      <h3 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-black tracking-tight text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
        Planes simples y <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-violet-400">transparentes</span>
      </h3>
      <p class="text-lg text-text-muted max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Sin costos ocultos ni contratos a largo plazo. Diseñamos tu presencia digital para que solo te preocupes por crecer. Cancela cuando quieras.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Cards -->
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-start">

      <!-- Plan Pro -->
      <div class="relative flex flex-col rounded-2xl border border-slate-700 bg-card-dark p-8 shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform duration-300">
        <div class="mb-6">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Plan Web Pro</h4>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-text-muted">Perfecto para empezar tu presencia digital.</p>
          <div class="mt-4 flex items-baseline gap-1">
            <span class="text-4xl font-black tracking-tight text-white">$20</span>
            <span class="text-lg font-medium text-text-muted">/mes</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-1">facturado mensualmente</p>
        </div>

        <ul class="mb-8 flex flex-col gap-4 flex-1">
          {proFeatures.map((feature) => (
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-slate-300">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-[20px] shrink-0">check_circle</span>
              <span>{feature}</span>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>

        <a
          href="https://wa.me/56942405123?text=Hola!%20Me%20interesa%20mi%20sitio%20web%20Pro"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="w-full h-12 rounded-lg border-2 border-slate-600 bg-transparent text-sm font-bold text-text-light hover:border-primary hover:text-primary transition-all inline-flex items-center justify-center"
        >
          Elegir Pro
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Plan Full (destacado) -->
      <div class="relative flex flex-col rounded-2xl border-2 border-primary bg-card-dark p-8 shadow-2xl shadow-primary/10 md:-translate-y-4">
        <!-- Badge -->
        <div class="absolute -top-4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-gradient-primary px-4 py-1 text-xs font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-wider shadow-lg whitespace-nowrap">
          Más Popular
        </div>

        <div class="mb-6">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Plan Web Full</h4>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-text-muted">Para negocios que buscan escalar rápido.</p>
          <div class="mt-4 flex items-baseline gap-1">
            <span class="text-5xl font-black tracking-tight text-white">$40</span>
            <span class="text-lg font-medium text-text-muted">/mes</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-1">facturado mensualmente</p>
        </div>

        <ul class="mb-8 flex flex-col gap-4 flex-1">
          {fullFeatures.map((feature) => (
            <li class={`flex items-start gap-3 text-sm ${feature.highlight ? 'font-medium text-slate-200' : 'text-slate-300'}`}>
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-[20px] shrink-0">{feature.icon}</span>
              <span>{feature.text}</span>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>

        <a
          href="https://wa.me/56942405123?text=Hola!%20Me%20interesa%20mi%20sitio%20web%20Full"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="w-full h-12 rounded-lg bg-gradient-primary hover:brightness-110 text-sm font-bold text-white shadow-lg shadow-primary/25 hover:scale-[1.02] transition-all inline-flex items-center justify-center"
        >
          Elegir Full
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
